Two collab marbles with @portland.dabber from his show this past weekend. Holler at either of us for more info. 💎
.
.
The first marble is 42mm and features some of Tanner's baller line work, dotstacks with some hidden uv, and a juicy opal. I did large cuts on this one, down into the rows of dot stacks, which allows the opal to shine between the rows of dots creating some fun effects. 
.
.
The 2nd marble is my personal favorite of the batch. Coming in at 41mm it features a double sided wag opal combo, with more of @portland.dabber linework and dotstacks. With this one i went with more of a traditional style cut with 3 rows of staggered 16. Topping it off with a large table to really make the opal pop. With a similar backside it allows you to contrast the optics with and without a faceted lens. 
.
.
Much love yall 💜💚♥️
.
.
